__e: Now they can study the Enterprise, add our technology to theirs, change the balance of power.
Captain, the 430 men and women onboard the Enterprise and the ship itself are endangered by these children.
You do not belong in charge of the Enterprise and I shall do everything in my power against you.
With Mr. Scott in a technical state of arrest, we've beamed aboard the Enterprise to continue the investigation.
Marta, I can help you. But I must get to the Enterprise to do that.
She would even murder me, the captain, the entire crew of the Enterprise, to keep you here with her.
The Enterprise is our ship, somewhere at sea.
And right now, the captain of the Enterprise is our problem.
Why do you think the Enterprise is my master?
